@Node "BI_REG" "PINT.guide/BI_REG"
@Next "BI_CRIGHT"
@Prev "BI_CRIGHT"
@Toc "Main"

Basic Information
*****************

How to register
===============

PINT now offers a free personal registration. To register, choose Register in
the Aboutwindow. Then enter your name and click on one of the registration
buttons. One is for registration through EMail and the other through Fido.

When the registration is sent a code will be returned as soon as possible. Then
just enter the supplied code in a new variable called @{"PINT.Registration" Link "CF_UMS_REG"} and
you are a fully registred user of PINT.

If you want to, you can have betareleases of PINT sent to you via email. 

@EndNode

